the king of paris ( russian : король парижа , translit : korol ' parizha ) is a 1917 russian silent feature film directed by yevgeni bauer . the film was shot in the cinema factory of aleksandr khanzhonkov in yalta . this was the last work of yevgeni bauer . as he worked on his previous film , for happiness ( ru : « за счастьем » ) , bauer broke his leg , and he shot this film while in a bathchair , but soon fell ill with pneumonia . he began shooting in early summer of 1917 , but he was soon placed in yalta hospital and on 9 june 1917 he died . actress olga rakhmanova finished the film .